covert
Discworld player help
covert

.SH Description:
.SP 5 5
The covert skills indicate your ability to do things without being
noticed.  They include the ability to hide, sneak, pick locks, and
ambush. Covert skills are the primary skills of Thieves and Assassins.
To see your current list of covert skills, type "skills covert"
.EP

.SH See Also:
.SI 5
sneak, hide, ambush, steal, lpick, shoplift, filch, palm, peek,
plant, slip, case, inhume.
.EI


